---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="QuickBooks integration - what does it do? | Help Centre | HedgeFlows"
  description="Learn what the HedgeFlows and QuickBooks Online integration does — data syncing, payment recording, reconciliation and more."
>
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">
        <a href="/help" class="hover:text-brand-green transition-colors">Help Centre</a>
        <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5" />
        </svg>
        <a href="/help/#integrations" class="hover:text-brand-green transition-colors">Integrations</a>
      </nav>

      <h1 class="text-[1.75rem] md:text-[2.25rem] font-bold text-text-heading leading-tight mb-8">QuickBooks integration - what does it do?</h1>

      <p class="text-text-body text-[0.9375rem] leading-relaxed mb-8">We summarise the activity that the HedgeFlows/QuickBooks Online integration enables:</p>

      <!-- ═══ Data Flow Diagram ═══ -->
      <div class="my-8 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-5 md:p-10">

        <!-- Logo Header -->
        <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-8 md:mb-10 px-6 md:px-14">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
            <img src="/assets/logos/HF-logo-gr.svg" alt="HedgeFlows" class="h-8 md:h-11 w-auto" />
            <span class="text-xs md:text-sm font-bold text-text-heading">HedgeFlows</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
            <img src="/assets/logos/integrations/qb-logo.svg" alt="QuickBooks" class="h-10 md:h-14 w-auto" />
            <span class="text-xs md:text-sm font-bold text-text-heading">QuickBooks</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Flow Rows -->
        <div class="space-y-2.5 md:space-y-3">

          <!-- Row 1 — bidirectional -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
            <div class="w-7 h-7 md:w-9 md:h-9 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs md:text-sm font-bold shrink-0">1</div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-brand-green text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Company & User Name</div>
            <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-8 md:w-16">
              <svg class="w-full" viewBox="0 0 60 12" fill="none"><line x1="8" y1="6" x2="52" y2="6" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="0,6 8,2 8,10" fill="#1f2937"/><polygon points="60,6 52,2 52,10" fill="#1f2937"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-[#2CA01C] text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Account details</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Row 2 — bidirectional -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
            <div class="w-7 h-7 md:w-9 md:h-9 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs md:text-sm font-bold shrink-0">2</div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-brand-green text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Contacts & bank details</div>
            <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-8 md:w-16">
              <svg class="w-full" viewBox="0 0 60 12" fill="none"><line x1="8" y1="6" x2="52" y2="6" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="0,6 8,2 8,10" fill="#1f2937"/><polygon points="60,6 52,2 52,10" fill="#1f2937"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-[#2CA01C] text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Contacts</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Row 3 — bidirectional -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
            <div class="w-7 h-7 md:w-9 md:h-9 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs md:text-sm font-bold shrink-0">3</div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-brand-green text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Invoices & Orders</div>
            <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-8 md:w-16">
              <svg class="w-full" viewBox="0 0 60 12" fill="none"><line x1="8" y1="6" x2="52" y2="6" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="0,6 8,2 8,10" fill="#1f2937"/><polygon points="60,6 52,2 52,10" fill="#1f2937"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-[#2CA01C] text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Bills, Invoices, Orders</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Row 4 — bidirectional -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
            <div class="w-7 h-7 md:w-9 md:h-9 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs md:text-sm font-bold shrink-0">4</div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-brand-green text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Account for Bank fees</div>
            <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-8 md:w-16">
              <svg class="w-full" viewBox="0 0 60 12" fill="none"><line x1="8" y1="6" x2="52" y2="6" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="0,6 8,2 8,10" fill="#1f2937"/><polygon points="60,6 52,2 52,10" fill="#1f2937"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-[#2CA01C] text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Chart of Accounts</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Row 5 — one-way → -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
            <div class="w-7 h-7 md:w-9 md:h-9 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs md:text-sm font-bold shrink-0">5</div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-brand-green text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Clearing and FX accounts</div>
            <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-8 md:w-16">
              <svg class="w-full" viewBox="0 0 60 12" fill="none"><line x1="0" y1="6" x2="52" y2="6" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="60,6 52,2 52,10" fill="#1f2937"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-[#2CA01C] text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Chart of Accounts</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Row 6 — one-way → -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
            <div class="w-7 h-7 md:w-9 md:h-9 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs md:text-sm font-bold shrink-0">6</div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-brand-green text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Booked Exchange Rates</div>
            <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-8 md:w-16">
              <svg class="w-full" viewBox="0 0 60 12" fill="none"><line x1="0" y1="6" x2="52" y2="6" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="60,6 52,2 52,10" fill="#1f2937"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-[#2CA01C] text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Bills, Invoices</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Row 7 — one-way → -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
            <div class="w-7 h-7 md:w-9 md:h-9 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs md:text-sm font-bold shrink-0">7</div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-brand-green text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Transfers</div>
            <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-8 md:w-16">
              <svg class="w-full" viewBox="0 0 60 12" fill="none"><line x1="0" y1="6" x2="52" y2="6" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="60,6 52,2 52,10" fill="#1f2937"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-[#2CA01C] text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Payments</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Row 8 — one-way → -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
            <div class="w-7 h-7 md:w-9 md:h-9 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs md:text-sm font-bold shrink-0">8</div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-brand-green text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Payment fees</div>
            <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-8 md:w-16">
              <svg class="w-full" viewBox="0 0 60 12" fill="none"><line x1="0" y1="6" x2="52" y2="6" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="60,6 52,2 52,10" fill="#1f2937"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-[#2CA01C] text-white font-medium text-[0.65rem] md:text-sm rounded-lg px-2 md:px-4 py-2 md:py-2.5 text-center whitespace-nowrap">Bank Transactions</div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- ═══ End Diagram ═══ -->

      <!-- Numbered Explanations -->
      <div class="space-y-4 text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body leading-relaxed">
        <p><strong class="text-text-heading">1)</strong> We source your company and user name for identification and sign-up purposes.</p>

        <p><strong class="text-text-heading">2)</strong> We source contact details for suppliers and buyers associated with foreign currency bills, invoices, etc. to populate our contact forms.</p>

        <p><strong class="text-text-heading">3)</strong> We source details of your purchase orders, bills and invoices to populate our Invoices &amp; Orders tables so that you can manage your currency cashflows and risks. This includes the status of the invoices. Only approved invoices can be paid via HedgeFlows.</p>

        <p><strong class="text-text-heading">4)</strong> We use your Chart of Accounts to identify suitable accounts for you to select in order to record our Bank Fees (optional).</p>

        <p><strong class="text-text-heading">5)</strong> We create HedgeFlows Clearing and individual foreign currency accounts to record transactional activity you perform on our platform (optional).</p>

        <p><strong class="text-text-heading">6)</strong> We update exchange rates on your Bills if you have booked exchanges for specific bills/invoices in advance on our platform. This helps reconcile the FX P&amp;L (optional).</p>

        <p><strong class="text-text-heading">7)</strong> We record transfers executed via our platform in QuickBooks and link them to specific invoices.</p>

        <p><strong class="text-text-heading">8)</strong> We record SWIFT (or other) payment fees you incur on our platform to the chosen QuickBooks account (optional).</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Back link -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
        <a href="/help" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[0.9375rem] text-brand-green font-medium hover:underline">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5 3 12m0 0 7.5-7.5M3 12h18" />
          </svg>
          Back to Help Centre
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
